Forever eCommerce
Forever eCommerce is a full-featured eCommerce platform built using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React, and Node.js) with Vite as the frontend build tool. It provides robust product management, cart functionality, and payment gateway integration.

Features
User Authentication (JWT-based authentication)
Product Management (CRUD operations)
Shopping Cart
Order Management
Payment Gateway Integration
Wishlist Functionality
Secure API Endpoints
Image Uploads using Multer & Cloudinary
Responsive UI with Tailwind CSS

Tech Stack
Frontend: React with Vite, Tailwind CSS
Backend: Node.js, Express.js
Database: MongoDB
Authentication: JWT
File Uploads: Multer & Cloudinary
Notifications: Toastr, SweetAlert2

